nd the utilization of solid waste resources and can be further applied in different environments such as high-altitude, high-cold mining areas and extreme environment agriculture based on the phosphorus solubilization mechanism of phosphorus tailings soil and the effect of the external field, so as to make contributions to the long-term sustainable development of agriculture.
